<title>USA: AMEX closing averages.</title>
<headline>AMEX closing averages.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-04-22</dateline>
<text>
<p>Prices on the American Stock Exchange closed lower in active trading.</p>
<p>The Amex Composite index closed at 544.96, down 6.51.</p>
<p>Losers beat winners 260 to 258.</p>
<p>The average price per share was down $0.15.</p>
<p>Preliminary volume was 24,734,355 compared with 17,091,825 on Monday.</p>
<p>(Prices official as of 1630 EST/2130 GMT)</p>
<p>((-- Wall Street desk, 212-859-1730))</p>
